te interests of the data subject; or<br style="box-sizing: border-box;">&bull; (3) is based on the express consent of the data subject.<br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;">In the cases referred to in (1) and (3), appropriate measures are taken to safeguard the rights and freedoms, as well as the legitimate interests of the data subject, including at least the rights to effect personal intervention on the part of the data controller, to present one&rsquo;s own position, and to contest the decision.</p>
